All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractEnumerableAdapter, EncancedListAdapter, EnhancedArrayList, EnhancedCollectionAdapter, EnhancedMapAdapter, ParamsMap, PropertiesBag, Range, TransformedEnumerable
public interface Enumerable<T>
extends Iterable<T>, Walkable<T>

Represents a unmodifiable collection-like interface that's still iterable and permits to query for the collection's size. In addition provides several methods for manipulating the data in the collection.
